.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbbef3b8f5ccd31e9c944d6983c3be053239b7b","tid":109221,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但大部分既食物都有奶類 真係戒清哂？</blockquote><br />\n點可能，只可以減少涉取<br />\n<br />\n想睇多啲就去google 搵 &quot;暗瘡 牛奶&quot; ，好似上邊有巴打講係有研究證明咗兩者係有關係"},{"pid":"373f6fc867ea5bb985898cfb6a9ce372e53def61","tid":109221,"uid":31164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"之前成日飲奶爆得好勁 戒左2個月而家得翻啲印一粒瘡都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f843df3889cc3e2f719b5e9d4d1788dbf4f3a300","tid":109221,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前睇過啲文獻，話牛奶同奶製品會誘發暗瘡，因為有嗰啲咩發炎因子，巴打可以考慮飲荳奶等非牛奶飲品，同埋試下戒一排奶製品（芝士、忌廉、乳酪），仲有戒糖，應該有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲以為荳奶係奶類製品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57081f1a10d522b1eef90223f692e75cc075cf4","tid":109221,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"男既話打少d飛機最實際"},{"pid":"d1eb77ec4209d481b21b7c4d31cd939fd37d2da2","tid":109221,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男既話打少d飛機最實際</blockquote><br />\n關事既咩 我剩係知放訓會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e069c522e88b9867abcd4e9cad5148f070a8176","tid":109221,"uid":352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但大部分既食物都有奶類 真係戒清哂？</blockquote><br />\n點可能，只可以減少涉取<br />\n<br />\n想睇多啲就去google 搵 &quot;暗瘡 牛奶&quot; ，好似上邊有巴打講係有研究證明咗兩者係有關係</blockquote><br />\n我試過足足一年半無掂過奶類 少少都冇。。。忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51ea64fe901bdbabd6e21f26a3752bd415c